listings.comment: Mahmodul was a pleasure to work with. Him and his team are thorough, very communicative, professional, and everything else you could ask. I don’t know much about developing websites but I feel as if I took a course, as now I know the language, process, etc as they kept me within the loop the whole time. I am very pleased with my website and will be working with Mahmodul again in the near future !!

They're probably better at much smaller projects that don't require that much attention to detail and feature richness so don't be put off by my review. Just stay away if your project is large and complex.

Cooperating with Md. is very good. His team is professional. They are quick, the answer right away and overall is nice. They have worked on a very difficult project that requires expertise and understanding and they got it both. Under my guide they have show professionalism so I will use them in the future.

Initially, they did a decent job delivering the project, but there were some revisions needed because it didn’t fully match the design file. I provided detailed instructions and even included screenshots to guide them, but they still struggled to implement the changes correctly. Toward the end, they tried to pressure me into accepting the project delivery, citing concerns about their rating, even though the work wasn’t completed as expected. Ultimately, they couldn’t finalize it to my standards, and I had to step in and finish it myself.
Great work and they understood what I wanted I changed some things and they were happy to facilitate the changes the team are very knowledgeable of web development
